{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_03_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依 3話 もう私のです",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――TRINITYAiLE、クリスマスライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The day of TRINITYAiLE’s Christmas concert",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、すみません――\nあのタクシーもダメか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Taxi—\nNo‚ that one’s full as well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.5902041117
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "乗車中のタクシーばかりですね……\nやっぱりクリスマスだからでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We just can’t seem to find an empty taxi…\nIt’s Christmas‚ after all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 15.3628569921
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すまない、やっぱりライブ当日に取材の仕事なんて\n入れるんじゃなかった。俺のミスだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry about this. I shouldn’t have scheduled\nan interview on the day of the concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "お世話になってる方なんですよね？\n仕方ないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t you have a good work relationship with them?\nDon’t worry about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8232613174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 26.426870664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "会場まで電車で行きますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Should we take the subway?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.426870664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "人が多い所はマズい……\nファンに囲まれでもしたら、それこそ間に合わない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to avoid crowds.\nWe won’t make it in time if we get bogged down by fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 34.6856237174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "天動さん、悪いけど徒歩でもいいか？\n人通りの少ない道を選んで行けば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to ask you to do this‚ Tendo‚ but are you up for walking?\nWe’ll look for a less crowded path…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "私なら、構いません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1011336724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 43.1480043968
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ前に体力を使わせて、すまないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to make you do this right before the concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1480043968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "会場まで五キロくらいですよ、全然平気です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The concert venue is just 5 kilometers away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1257141988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "毎日、レッスンで鍛えてますから\nさ、{user}さん、行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is nothing compared to my daily practice.\nLet’s go‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 56.1461679062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん、天動さん、こんなミスは今後絶対に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really sorry about this. I’ll make it up to you somehow…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1461679062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.7571203471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、いいんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. It’s okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7571203471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "こんな風に、クリスマスに誰かと一緒に歩くの\nなんだか新鮮で……楽しいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Walking together with someone like this on Christmas…\nIt’s such a fresh experience… I really enjoy it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "相手が俺で、さらに申し訳ない気持ちになったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apologies that you have to do it with me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9388889471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 70.9388889471
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.4524493058
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "……そんなことないのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Don’t say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4524493058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 78.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "会場の準備も気になるな\n電話で先に確認しとくか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder how things are going at the concert venue.\nLet me give them a call…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 83.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんは\nさっきから仕事のことばっかりですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}…\nAll you’ve been thinking about today is work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "え？　いけないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Er… Is there something wrong with that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ。大変仕事熱心でいいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ not at all. All good and well to be devoted to your work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "天動さん、もしかして怒ってないか？\n次からはちゃんとスケジュール管理するから、ごめん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo… are you angry?\nI’m really sorry… I’ll make sure I manage the schedule better next time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 102.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "別に怒ってませんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not angry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱり怒ってるよな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s definitely angry…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
